    {"course_id": 3, "title": "Introduction to Boda Boda Safety", "content": "## Introduction to Boda Boda Safety\n\n### What is a Boda Boda?\nA boda boda is a motorcycle used for passenger transport, parcel delivery, and commercial transport services.\n\n### Importance of Road Safety\nRoad safety protects riders, passengers, pedestrians, and other road users. Safe riding prevents injuries, deaths, property damage, and financial losses.\n\n### Qualities of a Professional Rider\n- Disciplined\n- Respects traffic laws\n- Maintains cleanliness\n- Honest and respectful\n- Rides responsibly", "order": 1},
    {"course_id": 3, "title": "Motorcycle Parts & Controls", "content": "## Motorcycle Parts & Controls\n\n### Main Controls\n- Throttle\n- Front brake\n- Rear brake\n- Clutch\n- Gear lever\n- Ignition switch\n- Indicators\n- Horn\n\n### Understanding Motorcycle Parts\n- Engine\n- Tyres\n- Suspension\n- Mirrors\n- Chain\n- Battery\n- Lights\n\nUnderstanding motorcycle parts helps detect problems early, improve safety, and reduce breakdowns.", "order": 2},
    {"course_id": 3, "title": "Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)", "content": "## Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)\n\n### Essential Safety Gear\n\n**Helmet**\n- Protects head during accidents\n- Wear approved helmets only\n- Fasten chin straps properly\n- Replace damaged helmets\n\n**Reflective Jacket**\n- Improves visibility during night riding, rain, and foggy weather\n\n**Gloves**\n- Protect hands and fingers\n- Improve grip control\n\n**Boots**\n- Protect feet, ankles, and lower legs\n- Sturdy construction required", "order": 3},
